content: I want to provide professional women of color with the top 8 holistic wellness mental and practical strategies that they can use that they are not learning from a corparate wellness program, are the program is not including them or not in depth enough. I want to Target professional women of color earning 6 figures or more and have under 10 employees. I want to use the book as a way to get people to see me as an authority in the holistic wellness and life coach space and ultimately book a call to find out how to implement this for themselves to develop peak performance and the life they dream of creating
